This is the package of all the resources used to produce
the NAACL00 paper on linear text segmentation.

bin		- Scripts for running the segmentation algorithms
data 		- Experiment data sets and results
doc		- Documentation and papers associated with the experiments
ebin		- Experiment scripts for batch testing
resource	- Data such as stopword list and pos statistics required by some of the algorithms.

Freddy Choi - 6th Mar 2000
choif@cs.man.ac.uk
http://www.cs.man.ac.uk/~choif